LuaJSON v0.6 Change Log

Fixes since v0.5
----------------

 * Encoder
   * Add support for encoding NaN/Infinity and \r
 * Decoder
   * Refactored most parts (string,object,array,number) out into separate
     configurable modules
   * Fixed support for empty objects, previous behavior was to not record a value
 * Build System/Tests
   * Added preliminary round-trip tests
   * Added some additional simple tests to help track down decoding errors
   * Added 'distcheck' target to test what would be distributed
